callgraph
Class AdjacenceElement

java.lang.Object
  callgraph.AdjacenceElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class AdjacenceElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Instances of this class hold a Signature and corresponding weights. It serves as class for the representation of the elements, that succeed the key of a AdjacenceList in a call-graph. Basically it is a Signature and the corresponding weights.

Author:
Christopher Oßner TODO a better solutions than using a single class for all hierarchy levels would be inheriting from an interface
